No. 10-8731. Ronnie M. Lyles, Petitioner v. Mary Ann Vial Lemmon, et al. 563 U.S. 929, 131 S. Ct. 1818,

179 L. Ed. 2d 794,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2680, April 4, 2011.

Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 405 Fed. Appx. 923.
